---
title: Beef Fillet Steak & Rainbow Carrots with Creamy Mushroom Sauce & Potato Mash
description: Steak, mash and mushroom sauce is a classic combo for a reason, and this dish highlights exactly why. Premium eye fillet is cooked just how you like it, and a creamy dreamy mushroom sauce adds rich umami flavour. The roasted baby carrots are not to be overlooked either, adding sweet brightness to your plate!
